2.9.7.name: wordpress/supra-csv-parser
2.9.7.description:
The purpose of this plugin is to parse uploaded csv files into any type of post. Themes or plugin store data in posts and post meta. This plugin provides the functionality to upload data from the csv file into the postmeta records which themes and plugins create. This plugin also provides the ability to import images and associate them to post as attachments or thumbnails. Manage existing csv files and promote ease of use by creating presets for both postmeta and ingestion mapping.

For general information regarding the plugin visit http://www.supraliminalsolutions.com/blog/listings/supra-csv/ .

Watch the detailed tutorials http://www.supraliminalsolutions.com/blog/supra-csv-tutorials/.
